### 1. Project Identity
- **Name:** What is this project called?
- **Purpose:** What are we building/doing?
- **Location:** Create here as subdirectory, or separate repo?

### 2. Project Type & Quality Gates

| Type | Typical Quality Gates |
|------|----------------------|
| Code | TDD, test coverage, CI, code review |
| Research | Reproducibility, source verification |
| Editorial | Human review before publish, style guide |
| Hobby | Lighter gates, fun over ceremony |

Make a judgment call based on what they describe.

### 3. Privacy Override

Default is hub's privacy model ({{PRIVACY_MODEL}}). Ask if this project needs different handling:
> "This hub defaults to {{PRIVACY_MODEL}}. Does this project need different privacy handling?"

### 4. Additional Primitives

The hub may already have MCAP, Panel, etc. Ask about project-specific needs:
> "The hub has [X] available. Does this project need anything additional, or should we keep it light?"

